  <brief_title>Evaluation of Aspen Spinous Process Fixation System and PLIF Technique for the Treatment of Low Back Pain</brief_title>
  <official_title>Evaluation of Aspen Spinous Process Fixation System and PLIF Technique for the Treatment of Low Back Pain in the Presence of Lumbar Instability and Degenerative Disk Disease</official_title>
